🖥️ Create First Window

---

💻 Example

```python id="first_window"
import tkinter as tk

window = tk.Tk()

window.title("My First App")

window.geometry("400x300")

window.mainloop()
```

---

📌 Explanation

| Method | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| `Tk()` | Create window |
| `title()` | Set window title |
| `geometry()` | Set size |
| `mainloop()` | Run application |

