🔘 Radio Buttons

Allow selecting one option.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💻 Example

```python id="radio_example"
import tkinter as tk

window = tk.Tk()

choice = tk.StringVar()

tk.Radiobutton(
    window,
    text="Python",
    variable=choice,
    value="Python"
).pack()

tk.Radiobutton(
    window,
    text="Java",
    variable=choice,
    value="Java"
).pack()

window.mainloop()
```

