🔧 Best Practices

✔ Separate GUI and business logic
✔ Use meaningful widget names
✔ Validate user input
✔ Use functions for event handling
✔ Organize widgets with frames

---

⚠️ Common Mistakes

❌ Forgetting `mainloop()`
❌ Mixing layout managers
❌ Not validating inputs
❌ Hardcoding widget positions
❌ Large functions handling everything

